data.description: Opportunity to own a beautiful home on a quite cul-de-sac, in an established neighborhood with mature landscaping, walking paths, and no thru traffic on Park Ridge Drive. This home boasts an open floor plan, with a formal living room, large windows and plentiful natural light. There is plenty of room to entertain or simply relax in the separate family room that opens to the dinning area and spacious kitchen with breakfast bar. Step outside into your own park like setting in the oversized back yard. Your imagination will be your only limitation for gardening, fun filled summer bbq's and catching the cool breeze under the large backyard weeping willow. 3 bedrooms & 2 full baths upstairs with a  1/2 bath down, along with a full sized 2 car garage make this home one you don't want to miss out on. Call now to set up your own private showing.
